programme.title: Lag Ja Gale Ep19
programme.desc: Drama ini mengisahkan perjalanan dua individu yang berbeza latar belakang, Shiv Dhooper, seorang usahawan muda Punjabi yang berjaya, dan Ishani Kulkarni, seorang wanita dari Maharashtra yang bekerja keras untuk menyara keluarganya. Mereka dipertemukan melalui perkahwinan yang diatur untuk membantu adik-beradik mereka, walaupun mereka mempunyai pandangan hidup yang berbeza. Dalam perjalanan mereka, mereka turut menghadapi pelbagai cabaran dan konflik keluarga. Akhirnya, kisah berakhir dengan mereka membina kehidupan bersama, menandakan permulaan kisah cinta mereka yang sebenar.

programme.desc: Sebuah rumah di tengah dusun tak dapat di robohkan sehingga di beli oleh faizal dan Yana. Faizal dan yana telah kehilangan anak perempuan mereka akibat kemalangan. Di dusun Yana bertemu Rinah iblis yang mendiami rumah tersebut. Rinah bagitahu Yana kalau dia boleh kembalikan anak yana yang mati. Yana lakukan ritual dan Naily benar-benar kembali. Faizal yang mulanya tak percaya pada hantu dan iblis akhirnya akur kalau rumah yang mereka beli itu benar-benar berpenunggu. Menurut cerita rumah itu kepunyaan Rinah seorang bidan yang banyak membantu gugurkan kandungan dan suaminya Hamdi seorang bomoh. Keduanya mati di dalam rumah di bunuh penduduk kampung.

programme.title: Hilang Kasyorga S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Rodi siasat sindiket penculikan, berdepan dilema antara tugas dan menyelamatkan Kasyorga. Reza sembunyi budak di rumah Kak Esah. Rahsia Mak Siti terbongkar. Rodi menjejak Rajoo di tengah laut.

programme.title: Petaka
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kemiskinan hidup keluarga Sham selepas kematian ayahnya. Ibunya menderita sakit kaki, manakala adiknya, Syikin tidak mampu ke sekolah kerana kekangan kewangan. Kedaifan keluarganya berubah secara drastik apabila Sham menerima tawaran bekerja sebagai pemandu lori barang di kedai perabot Haziq. Tugasnya hanya mengambil dan menghantar barangan perabot dari sempadan Thailand ke kedai Haziq di Alor Setar. Haziq bekerja di bawah Datuk Jamil.

programme.title: Transporter 3
programme.desc: Frank Martin terpaksa menghantar Valentina, anak perempuan pegawai kerajaan Ukraine yang diculik, dari Marseilles ke Odessa melalui Laut Hitam. Dalam perjalanan, dia terpaksa bersemuka dengan samseng yang ingin menggagalkan penghantaran tersebut

programme.title: Wok EP5 S1 Ep5
programme.desc: Wok disiksa suami sendiri, disiksa batin dan fizikal kerana nafsu binatangnya. Maimun semakin teruk dan akhirnya menghembuskan nafas seorang diri di rumah dalam keadaan menanti kepulangan wok. Sampai ke bandar, usop mencari sedaya upaya menjejaki wok.

programme.title: Munafik
programme.desc: Adam merupakan seorang pengamal perubatan Islam yang tidak dapat menerima hakikat isterinya sudah tiada di dunia ini. Kemudian, dia bersetuju untuk merawat seorang wanita yang tertekan bernama Maria tetapi perkara aneh dan meresahkan mula berlaku.

programme.title: Barajiwa EP1 S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Uzair dan Madi adalah musuh sekolah. Apabila Madi menghina kawannya Suresh, Uzair menyerang Madi. Madi membalas dengan menyerang rakan-rakan Uzair. Pidottrauma dengan serangan Madi tetapi Uzair cuba untuk menenangkan keadaan. Namun, apabila Madi menyedari bahawa CIkgu Sofi mempunyai sifatlemah lembut terhadap Uzair, Madi menyerang dan menyakiti Cikgu Sofi.

programme.title: Hilang Kasyorga S1 Ep1

programme.title: Kutuk
programme.desc: Maya, seorang jururawat yang baru berpindah ke sebuah asrama lama di pinggir bandar, mula diganggu oleh kejadian aneh dan menyeramkan. Dia kemudian menyedari bahawa asrama itu menyimpan rahsia gelap tentang sumpahan yang menghantui setiap penghuni yang tinggal di situ. Untuk menyelamatkan diri, Maya perlu membongkar misteri di sebalik kutukan tersebut sebelum terlambat.

programme.title: Barajiwa S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Abang Man memperkenalkan Uzair tentang kehidupan di KL dengan mengajarnya tentang perlawanan di gelanggang haram dan mendapatkan Uzair pekerjaan di tempat cuci kereta. Di KL, Uzair bertemu semula dengan Ajeeb yang kini menjadi busker jalanan dan tinggal di bawah jambatan. Hatta datang untuk melawan Uzair di gelanggang haram untuk menyelesaikan 'hutang lama.

programme.title: Wok EP5 S1 Ep5
programme.desc: Wok disiksa suami sendiri, disiksa batin dan fizikal kerana nafsu binatangnya. Maimun semakin teruk dan akhirnya menghembuskan nafas seorang diri di rumah dalam keadaan menanti kepulangan wok. Sampai ke bandar, usop mencari sedaya upaya menjejaki wok.

programme.title: The Sacred Riana: Beginning
programme.desc: Selepas memutuskan untuk tinggal sementara di vila kampung halaman mereka sambil menantikan kelahiran bayi pertama, pasangan Jun?ui dan Bi?roo menghadapi gangguan yang bukan sahaja melibatkan kenangan silam tetapi juga kehadiran misteri di rumah yang mereka duduki. Jun?ui mula terganggu oleh bayangan cinta lamanya, Jih?hee, yang hilang di vila itu, manakala Bi?roo melihat jejak-jejak asing dan merasa seperti sentiasa diawasi.

programme.title: Gemersik Berbisik EP6 S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Kimi, Daniel dan Suhana tidak percaya dengan Tasya. Hantu kanak-kanak tu datang mengganggu mereka pula.Menyanyikan lagu 'TepukAmai-amai' di sudut bilik yang gelap.

programme.title: Scoop
programme.desc: Tania, seorang wartawan menjalankan penyiasatan tentang kes pembunuhan rakannya, Johari yang menyiasat skandal syarikat kewangan. Skandal tersebut melibatkan bapa Sheila. Dibantu oleh seorang jurufoto, Norman yang ingin membersihkan namanya kerana sebelum Johari mati dibunuh, terdapat pertengkaran antara mereka berdua. Mereka pun mula menyiasat punca sebenar pembunuhan Johari.

programme.title: Gila Gila Pengantin Remaja
programme.desc: Pasangan remaja yang bakal menduduki peperiksaan SPM, Amir dan Mastura berikrar ingin berkahwin selepas tamatnya pengajian di universiti. Namun, Fandi yang juga rakan sekelas Mastura mencemburui percintaan mereka. SPM pun tiba tetapi Mastura terlewat menghadiri ujian Matematik dan berasa amat kecewa kerana menganggap dia telah pun gagal. Kakak Mastura, Anita pula ingin Mastura mencari calon suami yang kaya. Perasaan kecewa mula menyelubungi diri Amir apabila mendapat tahu Mastura ditunangkan dengan Fandi. Mengetahui perihal sebenar mengapa mereka akan dikahwinkan, Amir membawa Mastura lari ke selatan Thailand. Bermulalah kekecohan antara mereka semua dalam sekuel kepada Gila-Gila Pengantin ini.

programme.title: Boss
programme.desc: Tiga gadis bersama seorang kapten membanteras kumpulan jahat yang melanggar undang-undang. Mereka berhadapan dengan Malik yang menjalankan kegiatan pemerdagangan manusia. Pelbagai rintangan perlu mereka tempuhi apabila salah seorang anggota mereka, Clara diculik kumpulan tersebut ketika cuba menyelamatkan tahanan lain. Mereka pun memulakan misi untuk mencari Clara dan menjatuhkan kumpulan Malik.

programme.title: Hanny
programme.desc: Cinta Hanny dan Jeff dihalang oleh ayahnya, Dato' Mansor. Hanny pulang ke kampung bapanya dan ditunangkan dengan Faizal. Jeff memberontak dan hidup sendiri dengan mengambil upah membawa teksi setelah keluar daripada rumahnya apabila Dato' Mansor ingin menjodohkannya dengan Maria.Sofea yang juga kakak kepada Jeff telah mengupah seorang wanita bernama Sheila untuk mengintip perhubungan Jeff dan Hanny dan merosakkan hubungan mereka. Apakah kesudahan hubungan mereka berdua.

programme.title: Mira Edora
programme.desc: Mira Edora telah jatuh cinta kepada gurunya tanpa mengetahui hubungan silam gurunya itu bersama ibunya, Hapipah. Dapatkah hubungan mereka terus berkekalan setelah rahsia itu terbongkar?

programme.title: Amelia
programme.desc: Amelia menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan Fandy setelah mereka bertemu secara tidak sengaja di Cameron Highlands. Dalam masa yang sama ibu Amelia ingin menjodohkannya dengan Jefri. Amelia enggan menurut kehendak ibunya kerana Jefri seorang kaki perempuan. Bapa Amelia juga menentang keputusan itu dan bertemu Fandy untuk menceritakan segala yang berlaku. Fandy berasa bersalah kerana menganggap dirinya punca keluarga Amelia berantakan. Fandy mengambil keputusan untuk membawa diri ke luar negara dan hal ini telah menyebabkan Amelia terpaksa mengahwini Jefri. Selepas berkahwin, Amelia dijangkiti HIV daripada suaminya. Apabila Fandy mengetahui keadaan sebenar, dia ingin menebus segala kesalahannya terhadap Amelia.

programme.title: Kanta Serigala
programme.desc: Seorang gadis dengan impian yang besar diperkosa dan dibunuh. Shakira ingin menjadi seorang penyanyi yang terkenal kerana terpengaruh dengan penyanyi rock terkenal, Dania. Namun, malang menimpanya apabila dia telah dibunuh dua lelaki. Terkesan dengan kematian adiknya, Zarul ingin mencari pembunuh Shakira. Zarul memulakan misi untuk membalas dendam kematian adik kesayangannya.

programme.title: Harry Boy
programme.desc: Kurang kasih sayang dan perhatian dari keluarga, Harry Boy mula menagih kasih di luar. Dia bertemu Julia dan mula terikut-ikut gaya hidup Julia yang bebas. Ini mendatangkan kerisauan terhadap ibu dan bapanya apabila dia mula tidak menghadiri kelas dan pulang ke rumah. Kemudian, dia bertemu pula dengan Haryati yang telah mengubahnya menjadi manusia yang lebih baik.

programme.title: Nadia
programme.desc: Nadia mengikut ayahnya yang baru bersara daripada menjadi pegawai kedutaan Malaysia di London pulang ke Malaysia. Namun ibunya enggan pulang dan masih tinggal di London. Nadia memulakan pengajiannya di ITM dan menjalin persahabatan dengan seorang pemuda bernama Izam. Apabila Nadia mendapati ayahnya mempunyai hubungan intim dengan seorang janda kaya, dia berikrar untuk mengambil ibunya kembali serta memulihkan hubungan keluarganya yang terputus itu.

programme.title: Siapa Dia
programme.desc: Jasmin ialah seorang guru gimnastik kolej yang sangat terkenal dan disukai ramai jejaka. Saiful cintakan Jasmin manakala Sulaiman, jaguh dalam sukan taekwondo turut menyukainya. Dikacau oleh Frankie, seorang lelaki misteri telah menyelamatkan Jasmin. Ingin mencari lelaki misteri ini, Sulaiman dan Saiful keduanya mengaku menjadi lelaki tersebut - satu pertandingan diadakan untuk menentukan pemenangnya.

Jeff memberontak dan hidup sendiri dengan mengambil upah membawa teksi setelah keluar daripada rumahnya apabila Dato' Mansor ingin menjodohkannya dengan Maria.Sofea yang juga kakak kepada Jeff telah mengupah seorang wanita bernama Sheila untuk mengintip perhubungan Jeff dan Hanny dan merosakkan hubungan mereka. Apakah kesudahan hubungan mereka berdua.

programme.title: Boss
programme.desc: Tiga gadis bersama seorang kapten membanteras kumpulan jahat yang melanggar undang-undang. Mereka berhadapan dengan Malik yang menjalankan kegiatan pemerdagangan manusia. Pelbagai rintangan perlu mereka tempuhi apabila salah seorang anggota mereka, Clara diculik kumpulan tersebut ketika cuba menyelamatkan tahanan lain. Mereka pun memulakan misi untuk mencari Clara dan menjatuhkan kumpulan Malik.

programme.title: Mira Edora
programme.desc: Mira Edora telah jatuh cinta kepada gurunya tanpa mengetahui hubungan silam gurunya itu bersama ibunya, Hapipah. Dapatkah hubungan mereka terus berkekalan setelah rahsia itu terbongkar?

programme.title: Kanta Serigala
programme.desc: Seorang gadis dengan impian yang besar diperkosa dan dibunuh. Shakira ingin menjadi seorang penyanyi yang terkenal kerana terpengaruh dengan penyanyi rock terkenal, Dania. Namun, malang menimpanya apabila dia telah dibunuh dua lelaki. Terkesan dengan kematian adiknya, Zarul ingin mencari pembunuh Shakira. Zarul memulakan misi untuk membalas dendam kematian adik kesayangannya.

programme.title: Amelia
programme.desc: Amelia menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan Fandy setelah mereka bertemu secara tidak sengaja di Cameron Highlands. Dalam masa yang sama ibu Amelia ingin menjodohkannya dengan Jefri. Amelia enggan menurut kehendak ibunya kerana Jefri seorang kaki perempuan. Bapa Amelia juga menentang keputusan itu dan bertemu Fandy untuk menceritakan segala yang berlaku. Fandy berasa bersalah kerana menganggap dirinya punca keluarga Amelia berantakan. Fandy mengambil keputusan untuk membawa diri ke luar negara dan hal ini telah menyebabkan Amelia terpaksa mengahwini Jefri. Selepas berkahwin, Amelia dijangkiti HIV daripada suaminya. Apabila Fandy mengetahui keadaan sebenar, dia ingin menebus segala kesalahannya terhadap Amelia.

programme.title: Siapa Dia
programme.desc: Jasmin ialah seorang guru gimnastik kolej yang sangat terkenal dan disukai ramai jejaka. Saiful cintakan Jasmin manakala Sulaiman, jaguh dalam sukan taekwondo turut menyukainya. Dikacau oleh Frankie, seorang lelaki misteri telah menyelamatkan Jasmin. Ingin mencari lelaki misteri ini, Sulaiman dan Saiful keduanya mengaku menjadi lelaki tersebut - satu pertandingan diadakan untuk menentukan pemenangnya.

programme.title: Gila Gila Pengantin Remaja
programme.desc: Pasangan remaja yang bakal menduduki peperiksaan SPM, Amir dan Mastura berikrar ingin berkahwin selepas tamatnya pengajian di universiti. Namun, Fandi yang juga rakan sekelas Mastura mencemburui percintaan mereka. SPM pun tiba tetapi Mastura terlewat menghadiri ujian Matematik dan berasa amat kecewa kerana menganggap dia telah pun gagal. Kakak Mastura, Anita pula ingin Mastura mencari calon suami yang kaya. Perasaan kecewa mula menyelubungi diri Amir apabila mendapat tahu Mastura ditunangkan dengan Fandi. Mengetahui perihal sebenar mengapa mereka akan dikahwinkan, Amir membawa Mastura lari ke selatan Thailand. Bermulalah kekecohan antara mereka semua dalam sekuel kepada Gila-Gila Pengantin ini.

programme.title: Nadia
programme.desc: Nadia mengikut ayahnya yang baru bersara daripada menjadi pegawai kedutaan Malaysia di London pulang ke Malaysia. Namun ibunya enggan pulang dan masih tinggal di London. Nadia memulakan pengajiannya di ITM dan menjalin persahabatan dengan seorang pemuda bernama Izam. Apabila Nadia mendapati ayahnya mempunyai hubungan intim dengan seorang janda kaya, dia berikrar untuk mengambil ibunya kembali serta memulihkan hubungan keluarganya yang terputus itu.

programme.title: Scoop
programme.desc: Tania, seorang wartawan menjalankan penyiasatan tentang kes pembunuhan rakannya, Johari yang menyiasat skandal syarikat kewangan. Skandal tersebut melibatkan bapa Sheila. Dibantu oleh seorang jurufoto, Norman yang ingin membersihkan namanya kerana sebelum Johari mati dibunuh, terdapat pertengkaran antara mereka berdua. Mereka pun mula menyiasat punca sebenar pembunuhan Johari.

programme.desc: This series searches Borneo for top models, aged 16-25, competing for RM10,000. Castings in Sabah, Sarawak & Brunei (Ep1-3) lead to challenges (Ep4-12). Judged on beauty, passion, and skills, finalists face eliminations till one wins!

programme.title: Buang Dari Bau Ep9
programme.desc: Buang yang berasal dari Bau, Sarawak, hidup susah bersama ibu, kakak, dan adik. Ayahnya Zaini meninggalkan keluarga untuk kebahagiaan sendiri. Buang impikan menjadi pelumba perahu berjaya.

programme.title: Oppa
programme.desc: Menggambarkan seorang guru yang terperangkap dalam penipuan percintaan dalam talian, mendedahkan cabaran jenayah siber di Malaysia. Usaha pihak Polis Diraja memburu penjenayah menambah elemen suspen.

programme.title: Nada Siar Ep63
programme.desc: Sebuah program yang menyajikan kepada anda klip-klip video soundtrack yang terkandung dalam filem-filem klasik tempatan.

programme.title: Rampok
programme.desc: Seorang wanita bersenjata memasuki sebuah bank untuk merompak. Semua orang dijadikan tebusan, dan CCTV dimatikan. Inspektor Natasya mengetuai pasukan polis tiba untuk berunding dengan perompak tersebut. Setelah rundingan berjalan lancar, tiga tebusan dibebaskan. Perompak itu mempunyai latar belakang atau kisah peribadi yang sangat kuat yang membuatkan dia terpaksa memilih jalan merompak. Apakah rahsia sebenar di sebalik tindakan mereka?

programme.title: Abang Lejen
programme.desc: Dua beradik yang kehilangan ibu bapa mereka sejak kecil. Si abang sanggup mempertaruhkan nyawanya demi melindungi adiknya walau apa pun yang terjadi.

programme.title: Hayya 1: The Power Of Love
programme.desc: Rahmat, wartawan yang dihantui dosa silam, berhijrah jadi relawan di kem pelarian Palestin dan bertemu Hayya, anak yatim piatu. Pertemuan itu mengubah hidupnya, namun bila dia pulang ke Indonesia untuk berkahwin dengan Yasna, tercetus konflik emosi yang rumit, lucu dan tegang antara mereka.

programme.title: Hayya 2: Dream Hope And Reality
programme.desc: Filem sekuel ini menyorot trauma dan kehilangan. Hayya melarikan diri ke Indonesia lalu bertemu Lia dan Faisal, yang akhirnya menganggapnya sebagai pengikat rumah tangga mereka. Sementara Rahmat, Adhin dan Ricis terus mencarinya, rahsia keluarga Faisal terbongkar hingga tragedi besar berlaku.

programme.title: Girl In The Bunker
programme.desc: Kisah benar tentang Elizabeth Shoaf, remaja 14 tahun yang diculik lelaki menyamar sebagai polis dan dikurung dalam bunker bawah tanah. Dengan keberanian dan kepintarannya, dia berjaya menipu penculik hingga akhirnya diselamatkan

programme.title: Taikun
programme.desc: Mengisahkan dua lelaki bernama Tai dan Kun, sahabat baik yang hanya meminati pergaduhan dan mencuri. Apabila tabiat buruk mereka menyebabkan mereka bertembung dan memukul teruk ahli geng Pink dan Purple, Tai dan Kun kemudian direkrut oleh ketua geng yang kagum dengan kemahiran mereka.

programme.title: Bukan Cinta Malaikat
programme.desc: Berasal dari Bandung, Reyhan pergi ke kawasan konflik di Timur Tengah untuk kerja sukarela. Di sana, dia menolong seorang wanita Malaysia bernama Dewi dan jatuh cinta padanya. Apabila Dewi pulang ke negaranya, Reyhan bertekad untuk mencarinya dan melamarnya. Namun, Dewi sebenarnya sudah mempunyai kekasih. Dalam masa yang sama, rakan zaman kecil Reyhan, Aliyah, turut menyimpan perasaan terhadapnya.

programme.title: Peluang Ketiga
programme.desc: Zulaikha dan Yusuf telah menjalin hubungan sejak zaman universiti. Hubungan mereka berakhir apabila Yusuf tidak bersetuju dengan keputusan Zulaikha untuk menjadi penyanyi. Zulaikha kemudian bertemu Mikhail, lelaki baik hati yang sentiasa menyokongnya. Sementara itu, Yusuf meneruskan kerjayanya sebagai pelumba basikal profesional dan jatuh cinta dengan seorang wartawan sukan bernama Alya. Namun apabila Mikhail melamar Zulaikha, Yusuf mula cemburu. Mampukah Yusuf melupakan Zulaikha?

programme.title: Lelepati Adalah Komunikasi Cinta Yang Hakiki
programme.desc: Kisah ini berkisar tentang seorang gadis cantik bernama Tiara. Tiara tidak serius dalam pelajarannya semasa di universiti, menyebabkan orang tuanya marah. Akibatnya, dia dihantar ke kampung neneknya untuk menguruskan ikan lele. Di kampung tersebut, Tiara perlu menyesuaikan diri dengan persekitaran baru dan juga berdepan dengan seorang lelaki yang menyebalkan bernama Jaya. Jaya sering membuat Tiara kesal, namun dia mendapat sokongan daripada nenek Tiara. Namun, secara tiba-tiba, Tiara mula menyukai Jaya. Apa yang menyebabkan Tiara jatuh hati kepada Jaya?

programme.title: D'Academy 7 S7 Ep51
programme.desc: D' Academy 7 ialah musim ketujuh rancangan nyanyian popular Indonesia yang fokus pada muzik dangdut. Peserta dari seluruh negara bertanding dengan menyanyikan lagu dangdut, menunjukkan bakat vokal dan persembahan mereka. Sepanjang musim, mereka dinilai oleh juri profesional dan undian penonton. Siapakah yang akan menjuarai D'Academy musim ketujuh?

programme.title: My Heart S1 Ep74
programme.desc: Raisa yang patah hati selepas tunangnya, Rio, hilang tiba-tiba, pergi ke Jakarta untuk mencari jawapan. Di sana, dia bertemu Mike, seorang pelakon drama popular yang sebenarnya berperwatakan sensitif dan bermasalah, berbeza dengan wataknya di kaca TV. Perkenalan mereka secara kebetulan menjadi semakin rapat apabila mereka mula mengenali diri sebenar masing-masing. Namun, cinta mereka diuji apabila terbongkar bahawa ibu Mike, Rika, adalah isteri kedua kepada ayah Raisa, menyebabkan perebutan harta antara keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa Ep303
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa Ep303
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.desc: Wu is a senior police officer has always wanted a son to carry his family name and join the force. However, he and wife are bequeathed with four daughters! As a doting father, his chief objective is to help them find happiness in their marriages. In this charming drama, Wu & his wife become their daughters greatest haven, through the ups and downs they face as married women.

programme.title: Tales from the Occult
programme.desc: The movie consists of three tales about the horrors lurking in dark corners of the city. A young pop star goes back into depression when spooky things happen in her new home, an online influencer performs live in a mall, but it ends up being a livestream of his death, the residents of a tenement building battle a mysterious figure in the stairwell.

programme.title: Operation Bangkok
programme.desc: Military veteran Wu and undercover cop Ming rescue hostages on an island near Bangkok. Just as the mission is completed and they prepare to leave, Wu discovers his daughter has also been captured. Determined to save her, he stays with Ming to fight the thugs and rescue her.

programme.title: Beauty And The 7 Beasts
programme.desc: Teddy, once a renowned movie star, is facing a career decline. To make a living, he accepts five disciples to shape them into stars. Teddy's career regains momentum after he reunites with his long-lost daughter, but he is also confronted by a rival at the same time. His daughter and disciples decide to help him overcome this difficult situation

programme.title: Ride On
programme.desc: Master Luo, a washed-up stuntman, trains his beloved horse Red Hare to be a stunt horse. Due to his debts though, Red Hare may be taken away by the debtors. Master Luo has no choice but to seek help from his estranged daughter, and the incident ends up becoming a golden opportunity for them to reconcile.

programme.title: iGirl
programme.desc: Evan, Johnny, and Irwin are best friends. All three of them get dumped by their girlfriends one day and decide to find three robotic substitutes, the iGirls, as their new girlfriends. However, as time goes by, Evan finds himself falling in love with his iGirl

programme.title: Crisis Negotiators
programme.desc: Negotiator Wai becomes the prime suspect in a police murder case. He takes hostages at the police station and demands to negotiate with former negotiator Jun. As the two engage in a high-stake battle of wits, their expertise in psychological manipulation leads to a tense verbal sparring match, gradually shifting their positions and mind sets.

programme.title: MuMu
programme.desc: Mumu, a cheerful seven-year-old girl, lives with her deaf father in a deaf community and connects him to the outside world. However, their peaceful life is disrupted when her estranged mother reappears, pushing Mumu into the hearing world. Meanwhile, her father becomes ensnared by a gang that exploits the deaf to commit crimes.

programme.title: Romantic Dream
programme.desc: Dino meets his dream girl Mandy and falls in love with her at first sight. However, she disappears suddenly and he only sees her again after nine years, when she is already married. To overcome the pain of losing his love, Dino finds a guru with supernatural power to make him meet Mandy in his dream.

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his family's expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his family's reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: Echoes of the Rainbow
programme.desc: Set in Hong Kong in the 1960s, the story revolves around the family of a hardworking shoemaker Mr Law, with his happy-go-lucky wife and two sons - a talented elder son and an eight-year-old eccentric younger son. While their lives are not always smooth-sailing, the family sticks together and support one another through thick and thin.

programme.title: Mama's Affair
programme.desc: Former talent manager Mei Fung stays home to take care of her husband and son after retirement. She decides to re-enter the entertainment business to find her value in life, and successfully transforms a local restaurant delivery boy, Fong Ching, into a young pop idol. This makes her teenage son, Jonathan, intensely jealous of Fong Ching.

programme.title: The Grey Men 2
programme.desc: Triad boss Song seeks to whitewash his image and seize Laika's mayoral seat amid a regime change. He faces a funding shortfall despite colluding with officials, and gets his right-hand man and enforcer to commit crimes to boost his funds and power. Just as Song believes success is imminent, the dynamics between the three take an unexpected turn

programme.title: Wu Kong
programme.desc: Set 500 years before the Monkey King Wu Kong wreaks havoc in the heavenly kingdom, the movie tells the story of how Wu Kong who, unwilling to bow to his own destiny, sets out to rebel against the gods.

programme.title: Fly Me to the Moon
programme.desc: New Hong Kong immigrants Yuan and her sister face identity crises, poverty, and their father's drug addiction. Initially, the sisters attempt to appease him, but as they enter adolescence, they ultimately rebel and escape. Even as they separate from their father, Yuan finds his traits mirrored in her loved ones.

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: Limbo
programme.desc: Hong Kong is rocked by a series of brutal murders committed by a serial killer. Veteran detective Cham and rookie cop Will are assigned to the case. During the investigation, they encounter Wang Tao, who accidentally killed Cham's wife. Seeking redemption, Wang assists them in tracking down the killer, but her involvement puts her in grave danger.

programme.title: Beyond The Sin
programme.desc: The only daughter of Inspector Yan is brutally murdered, and her classmate Wen is arrested. Believing the case closed, Yan leaves the police force. However, when more girls are killed after Wen's imprisonment, Yan begins to suspect the real killer is still at large and vows to find the truth.

programme.title: Fight Back to School
programme.desc: The number one killer in SDU, Chow Sing Sing(Stephen Chow), is sent to a school to find a lost gun. His partner Tat(Ng Man Tat) pretends to be a school worker in assisting him. They recognize that some students are being closed with Fei, the head of triad society, and Fei traffics munitions. Sing steals and ignites Fei's munitions, Fei pledges to kill Sing...

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenix's (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: Operation Mekong
programme.desc: After it is discovered that the drugs seized on the Chinese ships had been planted by the henchman of a notorious drug cartel leader named Naw Khar, the governments of Thailand, Laos, Myanmar and China launched a joint task force to apprehend the criminal by sending a band of elite narcotics officers to the Golden Triangle to uncover the truth.

programme.title: My Wife is a Gambling Maestro
programme.desc: Natalie Yao Meng stars as the gambling queen, Ying Ying, who is a contender for the Asian God of Gamblers competition. But before the competition she is betrayed by her fianc and left for dead. Rescued by a young man called Gerrard, who suffering from amnesia, Ying Ying, must recover in time to compete in the big event!

programme.title: Old Fox
programme.desc: In 1989, young Liao Jie and his father save for a home, unaware of rising property prices. Frustrated by poverty, he learns from their landlord Old Fox who teaches him survival in society. Liao Jie ends up hurting Old Fox with what he has learnt, but his empathy prevents him from becoming like Old Fox.

programme.title: The Hedgehog
programme.desc: Wang's odd behaviour and quirky ideas make him a social outcast. His teenage nephew Zhou, who is ashamed of his stutter, becomes Wang's only friend. Together, these misfits challenge traditional family expectations and social misunderstandings, supporting and inspiring each other as they seek their own paths in life.

programme.title: The Gangster, the Cop, the Devil
programme.desc: The movie is adapted from real events. Detective Lin sets up a special unit to arrest the motorbike robber and the crime syndicate behind the thefts in Foshan. In the process, his pregnant wife is hit by a motorbike robber, leading him to uncover their revenge plan...

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as "Magic Hands" Ken, a legendary gambling maestro who is forced out of retirement when his daughter's safety is compromised by an international gambling mafia. In order to save her, Ken and his new protg Cool must work together to expose the evil mastermind by challenging him to a high stakes head-to-head battle of cards.

programme.title: Man On The Edge
programme.desc: On the eve of the 1997 handover, violence is rampant with triad forces causing chaos in Hong Kong. The triad gang leader assigns his right-hand man Ah Lok to take charge of the drug trafficking business. However, Ah Lok turns out to be an undercover police officer who unveils a shocking political conspiracy during the investigation.

programme.title: Last Suspect
programme.desc: Lawyer Chen receives a mysterious call demanding her to defend a murder suspect after her daughter is kidnapped, and is told that she can only save her daughter by winning the case. As she starts investigation with the police and evidence emerges, Chen discovers the truth and reveals the mastermind. Can she rescue her daughter in time?

programme.title: The Bride With White Hair
programme.desc: As Wudang disciple Zhuo Yi Hang confronts the Demon Palace, he reunites with Lian Ni Shang, the woman who once saved him, and their love reignites. Lian, a disciple of the Demon Palace, endures torment to be with Zhuo but is shattered when he accidentally injures her. A fierce battle between good and evil unfolds!

programme.title: MuMu
programme.desc: Mumu, a cheerful seven-year-old girl, lives with her deaf father in a deaf community and connects him to the outside world. However, their peaceful life is disrupted when her estranged mother reappears, pushing Mumu into the hearing world. Meanwhile, her father becomes ensnared by a gang that exploits the deaf to commit crimes.

programme.title: Ip Man 3
programme.desc: When some gangsters led by a ruthless American property developer force a school to sell their land, Ip Man fights to protect it. Subsequently, Ip Man is challenged by another Wing Chun master Zhang Tian Zhi for the Grandmaster title. Ip Man accepts the challenge for the sake of his family and disciples, and wins the duel for the title.

programme.title: Home Sweet Home
programme.desc: A school bus accident kills almost everyone on board. The bus driver got injured and partially lost his memory while rescuing one of the boys. To thank the driver, the boy's dad, Wang, brings him to live with the family in their basement. However, the driver soon discovers strange behaviours from the Wang's which seem to be related to the accident.

programme.title: The Boxer From The Temple
programme.desc: A young monk, The Kid, was expelled from the temple due to his crazy ways. After leaving the temple, he fights a cruel bandit's son and befriends a prostitute. As he fights for justice, his Crazy Lo Han Fist improves with every fight.

programme.title: The Enchanting Ghost
programme.desc: It is love beyond the grave, as a young scholar and his beautiful lover are torn apart forever by his dastardly uncle and his friend, who drive the girl to commit suicide... but with death comes revenge for the enchanting ghost. A spooky yet heart-wrenching tale...

programme.title: Pursuit
programme.desc: This movie tells the tale of Lin Chong, the Sung Dynasty's Chief Army Instructor who is framed by a corrupt official and has to embark on an exile fraught with danger. Helped by a monk, Lin Chong is finally able to take revenge.

programme.title: Inside The Forbidden City
programme.desc: Justice Bao discovers that Consort Li's new born son was swapped at birth and that she was expelled from the palace by Empress Liu twenty years ago. He sets Eunuch Guo up to confess his conspiracy with the Empress. Empress Liu is convicted for her act and Consort Li finally reunites with her son who is now the Emperor.

programme.title: The Magnificent Ruffians
programme.desc: A gang of unemployed martial artists seem to have their bad fortunes turned when the head of a local security agency hires them to take out the competition, who their new employer insists is up to no good. However, the men are being played for fools and have to take each other on until the last drop of blood is spilled.

programme.title: The Cave of Silken Web
programme.desc: In this third instalment of Shaw Brother's Journey to the West, Monk Tang San Zang is trapped by seven seductive spider spirits who are hell-bent on achieving immortality by eating him! Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing have to fight the spider spirits to rescue Monk Tang San Zang.

programme.title: Rape of the Sword
programme.desc: The film starts out with two students fighting for their deceased master's sword called the "Green Frost Sword". Han kills the other student, takes the sword and offer it to the king. The wife of the other dead student plots to take revenge, going undercover to retrieve the sword at the first opportunity in this tale of revenge and betrayal.

programme.title: The Delinquent
programme.desc: This is a coming-of-age tale depicting the lower class Hong Kong troubled youths in the 1960s and the societal issues that they face. Wang Chung is a hotheaded and rebellious teen who is tempted by the dark side, and have to unfortunately pay a huge price for it.

programme.title: Super Inframan
programme.desc: Transformed from a young laboratory researcher, the thunderbolt-fisted Inframan must battle Princess Dragon Mom who wakes up from hibernation to conquer the earth with her army of mutant monsters.

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: In 1973, the Hong Kong Heng Seng Index hit extraordinary peaks and people from all walks of life go stock market crazy. Meanwhile, Hong Kong's social problems build up without anyone paying attention to what are actually happening to the crazy lives of people, in this mad city that many call home...

programme.title: Tiger Killer
programme.desc: Wu Song is appointed as chief constable after killing a tiger with his bare hands when drunk. The wife of his brother Wu Da Lang, seduces Wu Song but gets rejected by him, and engages in an affair with a rich man. They poison Wu Da Lang when he finds out about their affair. To avenge his brother's death, Wu Song kills both of them.

programme.title: The Secret Of The Dirk
programme.desc: The inhabitants of the City of Liu are forced to flee when the vicious Black Tigers gang raids their city, but are able to hide all their gold and treasures in a valley. A team of swordswomen led by Liu wants to get their hands on the treasures before the bandits, but both parties will have to contend with the wandering swordsman Chou for them...

programme.title: Return of the Phoenix
programme.desc: An imperial minister Cheng betroths his pretty younger daughter, Ye, to his friend's son, Mu. His wife however, refuses to let Ye marry before her elder daughter Yan, who is ugly and undesirable. Yan is asked to pretend as Ye to meet Mu but scares him away. A rich guy who likes Ye meanwhile pretends as Mu to attend the wedding...

programme.title: Man Of Iron
programme.desc: A fearless fighter, Chou Lian Huan has risen to power in Shanghai with his exceptional combat skills. He risks his life for hostess Shen Ju Fang and embarks on a series of fierce battles against the son of a notorious triad leader and his gang, ultimately becoming a scapegoat in the gang's deadly turf war.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Ah Chiao, a village girl stranded in the city, befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are poor but happy, though Ah Chiao's fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she soon learns that money cannot buy one happiness...

programme.title: Heroes Shed No Tears
programme.desc: Kao Chien Fei is a young swordsman who wields a special sword with a teardrop marked on its blade. He is charged with averting an impending crisis in the martial arts world, but the villain, Zhou Tung Lai, wishes to become the ruler in the martial arts world, and launches a scheme to pit the various heroes against one another.

programme.title: The Pure and the Evil
programme.desc: Two teen girls, Rose and May, become close friends despite their different social backgrounds. The rich girl May moves to America but returns years later to see Rose, now a beauty queen and bar girl. Rose is immediately attracted to Fang's fianc and their relationship quickly deteriorates when Rose sets out to pursue him

programme.title: The Tea House
programme.desc: Big Brother Cheng fled from the mainland to Hong Kong, where he opened a teahouse in a housing estate, hoping to find a peaceful life. However, relentless provocations from local triad gangs go unaddressed by the police, prompting Cheng and his friends at the teahouse to seek revenge.

programme.title: The Dancing Millionairess
programme.desc: Peter was a key dancer in a dance troupe and applied to be the chauffeur of a rich girl, Betty. When he is rumoured to be her lover, Betty is furious and goes undercover as a reporter to investigate the rumour. They fall in love in the process, and after putting Peter through many tests, they finally seal their love with a dance.

programme.title: The Fake Ghost Catchers
programme.desc: Huan Zhu's ghost seeks help from Fake Ghost Catchers Bao Tuo and Zhou Peng, after a jealous suitor's ghost seeks vengeance by murdering her and now targeting her sister. Together with actor Wu Shun Chao who possesses a supernatural talent, they unite to protect Huan Zhu's sister from both mortal and spectral threats.

programme.title: The Shadow Boxing
programme.desc: Chan and his apprentice Fan transport zombies for a living and are hired to move nine zombies in one go. When two hop away, it is revealed that one is actually a man in disguise trying to escape his enemies. It turns out that both the disguised zombie and Chan are martial arts experts!

programme.title: Call to Arms
programme.desc: The aggressive and dangerous Chin Empire conquers the hard-put Chao kingdom while the Wei empire is drained of its heroes and paralyzed by an indecisive ruler. Adventure, intrigue, death and tragedy reigns before the triumphant clash of the armies.

programme.title: The Love Eterne
programme.desc: Ying Tai disguises herself as a boy to go to school and falls hopelessly in love with her classmate, Shan Bo. After Shan Bo realizes her true identity, he proposes marriage to Ying Tai. However, they are kept apart as she is engaged to another man. Knowing Shan Bo died in despair, Ying Tai is in deep sorrow and kills herself at his grave.

programme.title: Reincarnated Swordsman
programme.desc: A Wu Dang disciple Fu, kills the chief of Wu Dang Clan and frames it on the chief's illegitimate child, Yun. Fu then proclaims himself the new chief and orders the killing of Yun, who vows to avenge his father's death and learns the invincible silkworm martial arts style in order to defeat Fu.

programme.title: Between Tears and Smiles
programme.desc: Fan Jia Shu is a kind-hearted student who is smitten with Shen, a heart-rending love song singer. However, he is not the only one who has eyes for Shen. The General's henchmen are also determined to present the songstress to their superior as a gift. Fan receives help from an unexpected person just in time to save the woman he loves.

programme.title: The Flying Guillotine
programme.desc: Ma Teng is an assassin of the 'Flying Guillotine Squad', a group of killers commissioned by the Emperor Yung. When Ma starts to question the morality of his missions, he finds himself becoming a fugitive hunted by his former comrades.

programme.title: Hex after Hex
programme.desc: Hell may have no fury like a woman scorned, but hell literally, really has no wrath like a lusting ghost scorned! Cult classic director Kuei Chih-hung shoots the works with this amazing horror romance starring muscular "Venom" Lo Meng.

programme.title: The Water Margin
programme.desc: This is a martial arts epic directed by Chang Cheh. In the Sung Dynasty, the government is run by corrupt officials, so Sung Jiang gathers 108 outlaws at Mount Liang and establishes a band of patriotic heroes to end the repression of brutal overlords.

programme.title: The Yellow Muffler
programme.desc: Japanese director Inoue Umetsugu takes on the glitzy world of nightclub performers in The Yellow Muffler. The film depicts the struggle of two singing sisters, Ching-ping (Irene Chen I-ling) and Pai-hung (Betty Ting Pei) and ends when they are cast in a new movie.

programme.title: The Swordmates
programme.desc: Li asks his swordmate Wang to protect his family while he is away, but Wang rapes his wife and even has his convoy attacked. Li escaped but fears his daughter is still in danger, so he asks the nephew of his master to help protect her

programme.title: The Venus' Tear Diamond
programme.desc: Legendary rival jewel thieves Fragrant Night and Nocturnal Earl travel to Japan to steal the famous Venus' Tear Diamond. They fall quickly in love at first sight, without knowing the other person is their rival and is after the same prize. Who will get the diamond, and will it mean the end of their new found love?

programme.title: Marco Polo
programme.desc: Mongolian emperor Kublai Khan is being assassinated while meeting with the Italian explorer Marco Polo. Marco Polo is appointed to lead the troops for the emperor to wipe out the anti-Mongol rebels. Yet, he is touched by these rebels who are resisting the Mongolian invasion of their homeland. Will Marco Polo stay loyal to the emperor?

programme.title: Family Light Affair
programme.desc: Alfred Cheung Kin-ting returns to the screen with this seriocomic look at the clash of cultures which result when a Mainland Chinese peasant brings his family to Hong Kong. Family Light Affair, whose Chinese title literally translates as "City Lights", is the director/writer's warm-hearted memoir of street life back in the early 1980s, featuring an eclectic cast of pop music and kung fu stars who shine in their poignant roles.

programme.title: The Supreme Swordsman
programme.desc: After beating several famous swordsmen, Chin Wu Hsin of the Mo Shan clan challenges Supreme Swordsman to a duel, hoping to win his title, and is beaten and humiliated. The winner taunts him to find a Supreme Sword made by Old Eagle, a famous sword-maker. When his offer to buy a sword from Old Eagle, is turned down, he challenges Old Eagle to a duel, and snatches his sword in a foul play. Old Eagle's own son Shih Yen-peh vows to avenge for his father...

programme.title: DocFilm
programme.desc: Power of Secret Service - Intelligence agencies are influencing governments and spying on countries with no regard for the law. And they are able to remain nearly invisible, in the process. Are they the new superpowers? The last time intelligence agencies commanded as much power as they do today was during the Cold War. Technological innovations mean that more sophisticated warfare is now a reality. It is not just about Russia and the USA anymore. We may be entering a new era of unrest. The U.S. has lost more spies and informants since 2010 than at any other time since the Cold War. Leaders of German intelligence agencies also acknowledge that they have once again fallen upon tough times. Money, data and access are proving to be major factors in determining who actually wields power. The 2016 U.S. election made this clear: U.S. intelligence agencies are certain that Russian intelligence helped elect Donald Trump. But the U.S. has lost old spheres of influence and allies are increasingly pursuing their own agendas. Can President Biden make his country a force for order in the world, again? And what does that mean for political hot spots and potential conflicts with China, Iran, and Russia? And for allies like Saudi Arabia and Turkey? Will Western intelligence agencies regain the power they once exerted? Wars fought with drone and hacker attacks, increasingly delegated power, and surveillance could push these conflicts to their tipping point.

programme.title: DocFilm
programme.desc: Power of Secret Service - Intelligence agencies are influencing governments and spying on countries with no regard for the law. And they are able to remain nearly invisible, in the process. Are they the new superpowers? The last time intelligence agencies commanded as much power as they do today was during the Cold War. Technological innovations mean that more sophisticated warfare is now a reality. It is not just about Russia and the USA anymore. We may be entering a new era of unrest. The U.S. has lost more spies and informants since 2010 than at any other time since the Cold War. Leaders of German intelligence agencies also acknowledge that they have once again fallen upon tough times. Money, data and access are proving to be major factors in determining who actually wields power. The 2016 U.S. election made this clear: U.S. intelligence agencies are certain that Russian intelligence helped elect Donald Trump. But the U.S. has lost old spheres of influence and allies are increasingly pursuing their own agendas. Can President Biden make his country a force for order in the world, again? And what does that mean for political hot spots and potential conflicts with China, Iran, and Russia? And for allies like Saudi Arabia and Turkey? Will Western intelligence agencies regain the power they once exerted? Wars fought with drone and hacker attacks, increasingly delegated power, and surveillance could push these conflicts to their tipping point.
